data.description: Nestled within this luxurious residence lies an additional opportunity for potential income with a separate apartment, promising both versatility and financial advantage. Whether utilized as a guest suite, a rental unit, or a private retreat for extended family members, this apartment offers flexibility to suit your lifestyle needs.  Immerse yourself in the convenience of supplementary living space, complete with its own kitchenette, bathroom, and living area. With separate access, privacy is maintained for both the main residence and the apartment, ensuring comfort and autonomy for all occupants.  Imagine the possibilities of generating passive income through long-term rentals or capitalizing on the booming vacation rental market. This additional dwelling not only enhances the value of the property but also presents a lucrative investment opportunity for savvy homeowners.  Seize the chance to maximize the potential of your home and elevate your lifestyle with the added benefit of income generation. Explore the endless possibilities and make this exceptional property your gateway to unparalleled luxury living combined with financial prosperity. Schedule your viewing today and unlock the full potential of this dream home!
